# Repo-wide ignores (kept even though subfolders have their own .gitignore)

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/

# Virtual envs
**/venv/
**/.venv/

# Logs
**/*.log

